  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Hair Consultant",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Boosting sales revenue and profitability by achieving sales targets</li>\n  <li>Handle customer’s queries, feedbacks/complaints professionally</li>\n  <li>Conduct professional scalp analysis; demonstrate features/ benefits of treatments, services and products</li>\n  <li>Recommend packages according to individual needs and conditions</li>\n  <li>Constantly educate customers on the necessity and benefits of company’s treatments, services and products</li>\n  <li>Build rapport with customer and providing good customer service and needs in relation to hair &amp; scalp enquiries</li>\n  <li>Perform basic hands-on treatments when necessary</li>\n  <li>Updating of customer’s progress in the treatment card and computer system</li>\n  <li>Conduct regular stock-take, responsible for healthy stock level in store and stock ordering</li>\n  <li>Assist in display of merchandise, ensuring branding alignment and standards are maintained</li>\n  <li>Assist in other areas where necessary to ensure the smooth operation of the store</li>\n  <li>Other ad-hoc tasks as assigned by the Supervisor</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Certificate in any discipline</li>\n  <li>Experience and competent in sales with minimum 3 years of relevant experience preferably in beauty industry</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication skills (Bilingual) to liase with English and Chinese speaking customers</li>\n  <li>Sensitive to customers’ needs and attention to details</li>\n  <li>Strong sense of responsibility and urgency</li>\n  <li>Be self-motivated; high stress tolerance</li>\n  <li>Good team player, service oriented and proactive</li>\n  <li>Willing to work retail hours, on weekends and public holidays</li>\n</ul>",
